---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Careers – Aurapro | Join the team"
  description="We welcome applications from occupational, fire and environmental safety professionals and graduates. A 30-person nationwide team, nearly 20 years of experience, 48+ enterprise partners. Apply now!"
  canonical="/en/careers/"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-light to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="font-heading text-orange font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Join us</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 font-heading font-bold text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-heading leading-tight">
          Help us build Hungary's<br />
          <span class="text-teal">safest workplaces</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg lg:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed">
          For nearly 20 years, Aurapro Kft. has helped its partners meet occupational, fire and environmental
          safety requirements. Our growing team works nationwide – we welcome applications from
          <strong>experienced professionals and graduates</strong> alike.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#apply" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-orange text-white font-heading font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-dark transition-colors shadow-lg">
            Apply now
          </a>
          <a href="mailto:iroda@aurapro.hu?subject=Careers%20%E2%80%93%20application" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-teal text-teal font-heading font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Send your CV
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Numbers -->
  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16 bg-white border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-teal">30</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-muted text-sm lg:text-base">expert colleagues</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-teal">48+</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-muted text-sm lg:text-base">enterprise partners</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-teal">19</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-muted text-sm lg:text-base">counties we work in</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-orange">~20</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-muted text-sm lg:text-base">years of stable background</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who we're looking for -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-heading text-center mb-12">Who are we looking for?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Experienced professionals -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-sm border border-border">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-heading mb-3">Experienced professionals</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you are an occupational safety engineer, fire safety officer, environmental engineer or
              coordinator looking for new challenges in a stable, nationally recognised team –
              let's talk.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-body">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-teal">✓</span> Occupational safety engineer / technician</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-teal">✓</span> Fire safety officer / adviser</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-teal">✓</span> Environmental engineer</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-teal">✓</span> Health & safety coordinator</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Graduates -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-sm border border-orange/30">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-orange-light flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-xl text-heading mb-3">Graduates and career changers</h3>
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Do you have an engineering, safety or environmental qualification and want to get a taste of
              hands-on EHS work? <strong>You can apply as a graduate too</strong> –
              our experienced colleagues mentor you and we support you with further training.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-body">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Recent graduates from engineering / safety fields</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Career changers from other engineering / industrial safety areas</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Mentoring + internal training from day one</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-orange">✓</span> Part-time and internship positions also possible</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we offer -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-heading text-center mb-12">What we offer</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        {[
          {
            title: 'A stable employer',
            desc: 'A nationally recognised EHS company operating for nearly 20 years – partners include Audi, Siemens, Richter, DM, Primark, Porsche.',
            icon: 'M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6',
          },
          {
            title: 'Varied projects',
            desc: 'A broad range of occupational, fire and environmental safety work – you never get bored, always new industries, new partners.',
            icon: 'M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2',
          },
          {
            title: 'Mentoring and training',
            desc: 'You work alongside experienced colleagues – internal knowledge sharing, professional conferences, and up-to-date legal know-how guaranteed.',
            icon: 'M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222',
          },
          {
            title: 'Flexible working',
            desc: 'Partly on-site, partly from home – your schedule is tailored to your partner portfolio. A company car for on-site days.',
            icon: 'M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Competitive pay',
            desc: 'Market-level base salary + project bonus + fringe benefits. Your performance is directly reflected in your rewards.',
            icon: 'M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z',
          },
          {
            title: 'Nationwide presence',
            desc: 'We work in 19 counties. You can join even if you don\'t live in the capital – Budaörs HQ plus offices in Szekszárd and the countryside.',
            icon: 'M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex gap-4" data-animate>
            <div class="shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-teal-light flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={item.icon}/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-heading">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-body text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Apply -->
  <section id="apply" class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-[#919196] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl lg:text-4xl">How to apply</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white/85 leading-relaxed">
        Send your CV to the email address below, and in a few sentences let us know whether you are applying
        as an <em>experienced professional</em> or a <em>graduate</em>,
        and which areas interest you most (occupational / fire / environmental safety).
        <br/><br/>
        <strong>We respond to every application within 5 working days.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 inline-flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="mailto:iroda@aurapro.hu?subject=Careers%20%E2%80%93%20application"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-orange text-white font-heading font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-dark transition-colors shadow-lg">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          iroda@aurapro.hu
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+36704098764"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-heading font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
          </svg>
          +36 70 409 8764
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-white/60">
        We use your data only to assess your application and process it in a GDPR-compliant manner.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
